Uttar Pradesh
Nov 13, 2014
Rape
Description:
			A 36-year-old woman was allegedly raped by her neighbour after rendering her unconscious by giving her sedative laced 'prasad' at his residence here, police said today.

According to the police, the accused Kuldeep Sethi built a temple in his house where women often offered prayers.

The victim yesterday went to his residence to offer morning prayers when Sethi spiked sedatives in her 'prasad' and later raped her, police said.

He even threatened to kill her if she divulged the incident to anybody, police added.

A case has been registered, they said adding that the matter is under investigation.

